[_Salmonella enterica_ serotype Typhi is essentially the only serotype of the organism that is solely a human pathogen and is not zoonotic. It is spread through the fecal-oral route through contaminated water or food. In living conditions such as exist in the camp, in post-earthquake Nepal, or in flooding or drought conditions with an inadequate potable water supply, the infection will be found. - Mod.LL

